snippet.title: Top 10 Celebrities Who Married Awful People - Part 3
snippet.description:
Top 10 Celebrities Who Married Awful People - Part 3
Subscribe To Beyond The Screen: https://bit.ly/2txTtSd 
Watch Our Recent Videos Here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4_0B4cEcNRE&list=UU-wo9eCtm-_oSjDBFu_3JNg

Many celebrities manage to find a dream partner to spend their life with, but not all celebs are so lucky in the world of love. The reality is that many of the nicest stars have found themselves in crummy relationships with a partner who isn't such a nice person, to say the least. These relationships often end in disaster, and many times involve cheating, bullying, and even worse.
These stars take "love is blind" to a whole new level, these are the Top 10 Celebrities Who Married Awful People - Part 3 here on Top 10 Beyond the Screen!
